    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.搭建weex环境</p><p>1).安装node.js，官网下载<br><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></p><p>2).安装weex-toolkit</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g weex-toolkit</span><br><span class="line"> weex -v //查看当前weex版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2172404-e8a97b91301ac7e9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="weex -v.png"></p><p>2.初始化</p> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">weex create awesome-project</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.开发</p><p>1). 安装项目依赖<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2). 开启 watch 模式和静态服务器</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run dev  // 开启 watch 模式</span><br><span class="line">npm run serve // 静态服务器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3).  查看页面</p><p>打开浏览器输入 <a href="http://10.16.15.81:8081/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://10.16.15.81:8081/</a> ，看到页面</p><p><img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/2172404-f6eca9e9109cf29e.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="weex H5.png"></p>]]></content>
    
